<section class="landing-faq" id="faq">
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="faq-split">
            <div class="faq-header reveal-left">
                <span class="section-tag">FAQ</span>
                <h2>Common questions,<br><strong>straight answers.</strong></h2>
                <p>Everything you need to know about getting started with Fund-Raise.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-list reveal-right">
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>What is Fund-Raise?</summary>
                    <p>Fund-Raise is a fundraising intelligence platform built for foundations and nonprofits running Blackbaud RE NXT. It combines 30+ pre-built dashboards, AI-powered conversational analytics, donor scoring, and 6 writing tools into one platform — replacing the patchwork of Insight Designer, MissionBI, Crystal Reports, and standalone AI tools.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How does the AI assistant work?</summary>
                    <p>Ask Fund-Raise uses Claude by Anthropic to answer natural-language questions about your fundraising data. It can look up donors in your Blackbaud CRM via the SKY API, analyze trends from your imported data, compare campaigns year-over-year, detect anomalies, and generate insights. It also supports image uploads — attach a screenshot and ask about it.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Is my data secure?</summary>
                    <p>Yes. All data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest. Authentication is handled through Google OAuth 2.0, and we use role-based access control to ensure users only see data appropriate to their role. We never sell or share your data with third parties. The AI assistant processes queries in real-time and does not retain your data.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Do I need Blackbaud RE NXT?</summary>
                    <p>No. Blackbaud integration is optional. Fund-Raise works as a standalone platform using uploaded CSV/Excel data. The Blackbaud integration adds real-time CRM lookups for organizations that use Raiser's Edge NXT, but all 30+ dashboards and analytics work with imported data alone.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How do I get my data in?</summary>
                    <p>Two options: (1) Drag-and-drop CSV or Excel files — Fund-Raise auto-maps columns and processes in the background. Import history is tracked, and you can browse any past upload date. (2) Connect to Blackbaud RE NXT via OAuth for real-time constituent lookups through the SKY API.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How much does Fund-Raise cost?</summary>
                    <p>Fund-Raise is $199/month. Pay annually and save 15% — that's $2,030/year billed once, instead of $2,388. Everything is included: 30+ dashboards, Ask Fund-Raise AI assistant, 6 writing tools, team collaboration, board report PDF generation, CSV exports, Blackbaud RE NXT integration, and all future updates. No per-user fees. No add-ons.</p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
